  "description": "This mod adds matrix blocks (green 1s and 0s) to your game. You can decorate your house (if you like computers, that is).",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/matrix-blocks\"><img alt=\"Matrix Blocks\" width=200 src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ok-coder1/matrix-blocks/refs/heads/master/img/icon.png\"></a>\n\n<h1 align=\"center\">Matrix Blocks <br>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ok-coder1/matrix-blocks/actions/workflows/build.yml\"><img alt=\"GitHub Actions Build Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/ok-coder1/matrix-blocks/build.yml\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/matrix-blocks\"><img alt=\"Modrinth Game Versions\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/game-versions/vqVVYkM8\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ok-coder1/matrix-blocks/blob/master/LICENSE\"><img alt=\"GitHub License\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/ok-coder1/matrix-blocks\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/matrix-blocks\"><img alt=\"Modrinth Page\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/matrix-blocks\"><img alt=\"CurseForge Page\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/\"><img alt=\"Available on Fabric\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img alt=\"Requires Fabric API\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\"></a>\n</h1>\n\n\nThis mod adds blocks with green 1s and 0s aka the matrix :3.\n\n<hr>\n\nYou can use this mod to **decorate** your creations in Minecraft (that is, if you like computers).\n\nI'm planning to add computers and smartphones, etc. to this mod sometime in the near future.\n\n## What it adds\nIt adds blocks, stairs, slabs, buttons, and more! Try it out!\n\n## Notes\nUses stock images. Thanks to PixilartDude for the [matrix image](https://www.pixilart.com/art/the-matrix-a1673a6e4ffcb1e). I forgot from where I got the fading matrix image, but thanks to the guy who made that!\n\n##### This was made for Hackcraft XD.",
